This project is config-driven.

Before generating or modifying any section, component, or layout file:

1. Inspect:
   - config/site.ts
   - config/sections.ts

2. Sections must:
   - Match a valid HomeSectionId
   - Be selectable via HOME_SECTION_IDS
   - Support variant naming conventions (section-id, section-id-v2, etc.)
   - Not introduce new unregistered section IDs

3. Components must:
   - Use values from siteConfig (business info, branding, navigation)
   - Respect siteConfig.branding.colors
   - Use siteConfig.navigation for menus

4. Never hardcode:
   - Business name
   - Phone
   - Address
   - Colors
   - Navigation links
   - Section order

All reusable data must come from the config system.
